, 
12b
). G1SS tapering slightly from wide basal margin to relatively wide distal margin (0.6 
x
SS basal margin); dorsal face with broad dorsal membrane (maximum width 0.1 
x
SS length) at TA/SS junction (
Fig. 11b
). G2TA long (TA/SS = 0.40), flagellum-like, almost as long as G2SS. Mature between CW 13-17 mm.
